&lt;li&gt;Maintains and monitors metrics relevant to team activities such as PSURs, CERs, Safety Surveillance activities, Literature Searches, Literatures Reviews, Compliance Activities, providing visibility of issues and enable corrective and preventive action to be taken as needed&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
