&lt;li&gt;Ensure consistency with ICH, GCP, GPP, and company standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct literature reviews and evidence synthesis from peer-reviewed journals and congress proceedings.&lt;/li&gt;
